     F** EDSR6M ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY - SAVE AB#PP6M TO AB#PPE1        *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)                                 *
     F*           06/19/2019                               *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     FAB#PP6M IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PPE1 O   E                    DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140D#TIME
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C                     TIME           D#TIME
      * SAVE AB#PP6M
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLAB#PP6M
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ AB#PP6M                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     M6CRDT
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       M6CRTM
     C                     WRITEAB#PPE11
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
